lead_paragraph: Brianna Turner had 19 points, seven rebounds and five blocks, leading No. 2 Notre Dame to a 79-61 win over Michigan State on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Turner-Led No. 2 Notre Dame Beats Michigan State 79-61
